OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772100321
OL,3,CMan admits sending threatening hoax
OL,4,Cemails to schools
OL,6,FA man has admitted to sending
OL,7,Fthreatening hoax emails that sent
OL,8,Fthree all-girls schools into lockdown.
OL,10,FDarren Rigby, 21, pleaded guilty to
OL,11,Fthree counts of sending communication
OL,12,Fthreatening death or serious harm
OL,13,Frelating to the emails sent to the
OL,14,Fschools in Merseyside in January 2026.
OL,16,FRigby sent a first email to Holly
OL,17,FLodge Girls' College in West Derby on
OL,18,F19 January, and it was reported the
OL,19,Fschool went into "immediate lockdown".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
