FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772100321
OL,3,CMan admits sending threatening hoax
OL,4,Cemails to schools
OL,6,FThe school's headteacher Andy Keen
OL,7,Fsaid the incident lasted 50 minutes
OL,8,Ffrom receipt of the email to the
OL,9,Fdismissal of students. He added he was
OL,10,Fconfident the response was "robust and
OL,11,Fefficient".
OL,13,FIn a statement he added: "We
OL,14,Funderstand the potential distress and
OL,15,Falarm such threats cause parents, who
OL,16,Funderstandably are worried about their
OL,17,Fchildren.
OL,19,F"Sadly, such threats to schools are
OL,20,Fnot unusual and are designed to cause
OL,21,Fdisruption and worry."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772100321
OL,3,CMan admits sending threatening hoax
OL,4,Cemails to schools
OL,6,FFollowing the incident, it was
OL,7,Freported that West Derby School, near
OL,8,FHolly Lodge, had announced it would
OL,9,Fnot be opening on 21 January, after it
OL,10,Falso received an alleged malicious
OL,11,Fcommunication. The school remained
OL,12,Fshut for the entire day before
OL,13,Freopening the following day.
OL,15,FGreenbank High School in Southport was
OL,16,Falso forced to lock all doors and
OL,17,Fwindows, as well as cancelling outdoor
OL,18,Flessons, when staff allegedly received
OL,19,Fa similar hoax email on 23 January.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772100321
OL,3,CMan admits sending threatening hoax
OL,4,Cemails to schools
OL,6,FIn a statement issued via Sefton
OL,7,FCouncil, headteacher Davina Aspinall
OL,8,Fsaid: "Like other schools in the
OL,9,Fregion we received email
OL,10,Fcorrespondence today of a concerning
OL,11,Fnature.
OL,13,F"While both Merseyside Police and the
OL,14,FSouthport Learning Trust believe this
OL,15,Fcorrespondence to be a hoax,
OL,16,Fabsolutely no risks were taken and we
OL,17,Fimmediately enacted our shelter mode
OL,18,Fpolicy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772100321
OL,3,CMan admits sending threatening hoax
OL,4,Cemails to schools
OL,6,F"During shelter mode all education
OL,7,Fcontinues as normal with added
OL,8,Fsecurity measures including the
OL,9,Flocking of all internal doors and
OL,10,Fwindows. Any pupils taking lessons
OL,11,Foutside were brought indoors as a
OL,12,Fprecaution. We immediately contacted
OL,13,Fparents and carers to alert them to
OL,14,Fthis matter."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
