PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772100321
OL,3,CMan admits sending threatening hoax
OL,4,Cemails to schools
OL,6,FThree days later The Belvedere Academy
OL,7,Fin Toxteth reported receiving a
OL,8,Fsimilar email which resulted in the
OL,9,Fschool being placed in lockdown.
OL,10,FMerseyside Police later confirmed
OL,11,Fofficers believed it was another
OL,12,Falleged hoax.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772100321
OL,3,CMan admits sending threatening hoax
OL,4,Cemails to schools
OL,6,FMerseyside Police and Liverpool City
OL,7,FCouncil issued a joint statement which
OL,8,Fsaid: "Enquiries regarding the cause
OL,9,Fof these threats are ongoing, but at
OL,10,Fthis stage we believe they are hoax
OL,11,Fmessages and there have been no
OL,12,Fcredible threats in Liverpool.
OL,13,FOfficers are continuing to provide
OL,14,Freassurance and advice to those
OL,15,Fschools.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772100321
OL,3,CMan admits sending threatening hoax
OL,4,Cemails to schools
OL,6,F"The safety of students and staff is
OL,7,Four highest priority. We'd like to
OL,8,Fthank parents and carers for their
OL,9,Fpatience and understanding and ask
OL,10,Fthat they continue to follow advice
OL,11,Fand guidance from their child's
OL,12,Findividual schools."
OL,14,FRigby appeared in Liverpool
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court on 30 January,
OL,16,Fwhere he also pleaded guilty to drug
OL,17,Fcharges and possession of an offensive
OL,18,Fweapon in a private place; a baton.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
