FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772100321
OL,3,CMan admits sending threatening hoax
OL,4,Cemails to schools
OL,6,FHe was remanded into custody to be
OL,7,Fsentenced at Liverpool Crown Court on
OL,8,F27 February.
OL,10,FSpeaking after he was charged,
OL,11,FMerseyside Police Detective Inspector
OL,12,FJohn Black said: "I hope our
OL,13,Finvestigation reassures our
OL,14,Fcommunities how seriously we take
OL,15,Fthese reports.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
