OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772100321
OL,3,CMan admits sending threatening hoax
OL,4,Cemails to schools
OL,6,F"I would like to take this opportunity
OL,7,Fto once again reassure parents and
OL,8,Fcarers that schools across Merseyside
OL,9,Fhave well established and practiced
OL,10,Fprocedures to keep children and school
OL,11,Fstaff safe when schools are made aware
OL,12,Fof potential incidents or threats.
OL,14,F"This work will continue and as a
OL,15,Fpolice force we will always look to
OL,16,Fprovide advice to schools if required
OL,17,Fand carry out enquiries if such
OL,18,Fincidents occur in the future."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
